<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>{{title}}</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #161816;
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
            background-color: #f4f7f6;
        }
        .container {
            background: white;
            padding: 30px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            box-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
        }
        .header {
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
            padding-bottom: 20px;
            border-bottom: 2px solid #7eed5e;
        }
        .logo {
            font-size: 24px;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #7eed5e;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }
        .title {
            color: #161816;
            font-size: 24px;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }
        .content {
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }
        .greeting {
            font-size: 18px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        .message {
            margin-bottom: 25px;
            line-height: 1.8;
        }
        .verification-btn {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 15px 30px;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f5e800 0%, #7eed5e 100%);
            color: #161816;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 5px;
            font-weight: bold;
            text-align: center;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        .verification-btn:hover {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #7eed5e 0%, #3F634D 100%);
        }
        .alternative-link {
            background-color: #f4f7f6;
            padding: 15px;
            border-radius: 5px;
            margin: 20px 0;
            word-break: break-all;
        }
        .footer {
            text-align: center;
            margin-top: 30px;
            padding-top: 20px;
            border-top: 1px solid #7eed5e;
            color: #3F634D;
            font-size: 14px;
        }
        .security-note {
            background-color: #fff9e6;
            border: 1px solid #f5e800;
            padding: 15px;
            border-radius: 5px;
            margin: 20px 0;
            font-size: 14px;
            color: #3F634D;
        }
        @media (max-width: 600px) {
            body {
                padding: 10px;
            }
            .container {
                padding: 20px;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <div class="logo">The Skill Club</div>
            <h1 class="title">{{title}}</h1>
        </div>
        
        <div class="content">
            <div class="greeting">Hello {{name}},</div>
            
            <div class="message">
                <p>Welcome to The Skill Club! We're excited to have you join our community of talented professionals.</p>
                
                <p>To complete your registration and start exploring opportunities, please verify your email address by clicking the button below:</p>
            </div>
            
            <div style="text-align: center;">
                <a href="{{verificationLink}}" class="verification-btn">Verify Email Address</a>
            </div>
            
            <div class="security-note">
                <strong>Security Note:</strong> This verification link will expire in 24 hours for your security. If you didn't create an account with us, please ignore this email.
            </div>
            
            <div class="message">
                <p>If the button above doesn't work, you can copy and paste the following link into your browser:</p>
            </div>
            
            <div class="alternative-link">
                {{verificationLink}}
            </div>
            
            <div class="message">
                <p>Once verified, you'll be able to:</p>
                <ul>
                    <li>Complete your professional profile</li>
                    <li>Browse and apply for jobs</li>
                    <li>Take skill assessments</li>
                    <li>Connect with top companies</li>
                    <li>Access exclusive career resources</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
            
            <div class="message">
                <p>If you have any questions or need assistance, feel free to contact our support team.</p>
                
                <p>Best regards,<br>
                The Skill Club Team</p>
            </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="footer">
            <p>&copy; {{year}} The Skill Club. All rights reserved.</p>
            <p>This email was sent to {{email}}</p>
            <p>{{baseURL}}</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
